## 📋 `.gitignore` File

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.so
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.venv/
env/
venv/

# Environment (SECRETS - NEVER COMMIT)
.env
*.env.local
*.env.production

# Qdrant storage (large binary data)
qdrant_storage/

# Audit logs (runtime data, not code)
audit_logs/
email_log.json

# Models (large files - use Git LFS or exclude)
*.bin
*.pth
*.gguf
*.safetensors
!compliance_lora/adapter_model.safetensors  # Our small LoRA is OK

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

